PHP Strict

A set of simple utilities for adding strictness to your PHP,
using facilities already built into the language.

Trait IMSoP\Strict\Properties
    Declare that the list of properties in your class is complete,
    and should not be modified at runtime. Eliminates the possibility
    of

Trait IMSoP\Strict\StaticClass
    Declare that a class consists only of static members, and should
    not be constructed.
    Does not make the entire class "final", but does prevent non-static descendant classes.
    See also the rejected RFC https://wiki.php.net/rfc/abstract_final_class